Star Wars Behind the Magic: The Insider's Guide to Star Wars

Developer(s):  LucasArts
Publisher(s):  LucasArts
Release date:  Fall 1998
Genre:  Behind the scenes
Modes:  Single player
Platform(s):  PC

NOTE:  Behind The Magic runs in Windows XP, Windows 98 and Windows 95. It will run in 64 bit Windows 7 only if the 16 bit Installer can be bypassed. The work around is to first install in an older Windows such as XP, then copy the BTM folder over to the Windows 7 computer. A simple update of the Windows 7 Registry allows the program to run.


